pull.title: [depends] Fix QT build on OSX
pull.body:
This should be enough to fix the depends QT build on OSX.

cc @theuni 

Fixes #9126

events.body: @fanquake Only the second was actually needed for me, is the libcocoa.a change necessary now that we aren't missing symbols? I kinda doubt it, since it's got a typo (p -> cp) :P
